    <defName>RNApparel_CVCHelmet_LMM</defName>
    <label>CVC helmet LMCT</label>
    <description>Tank Crewman are worst hit by secondary fragments, shrapnel’s and blast related head injuries as they are confined within the tanks hull and are subjected to rigorous severity of the combat zone. CVC helmets are given a special shape to adapt to various communication systems, headsets /ear muffs etc.
	
